com.blockwithme.util.xtend

Class BooleanExtension

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.blockwithme.util.shared.Preconditions
      • com.blockwithme.util.xtend.JavaUtilLoggingExtension
        • com.blockwithme.util.xtend.ScalarExtension
          • com.blockwithme.util.xtend.BooleanExtension
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MathExtension

    public class BooleanExtension
extends ScalarExtension
    Xtend Extension related to Boolean values. Due to Xtend currently badly lacking unary operators, all values are converted to "not true?" instead of "true?"
    Author:
    monster
